Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBSampleDefectIDs

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBSampleDefectIDs
public class JDBSampleDefectIDs extends Object
The JDBSampleDefects class is used to insert/update/delete records in the table APP_SAMPLE_DEFECT_ID. This table contains a list of valid reasons which can be assigned to the Pallet Sample.
